What you’ll learn:

Python NumPy Hello Everyone! In this course I’ll cover the basics of using number and have several interactive course videos that will challenge you to learn how to use NumPy. I’ve always included a python course as well, but that’s just bonus content (in case you haven’t used python before.)

We’ll cover:

– Why use NumPy?

– NumPy Arrays

-Array Math

– Array Indexing

– Advanced Indexing

– Broadcasting

& much more!

Learn NumPy Fundamentals (Python Library for Data Science) https://futurenewsforyou.com/learn-numpy-fundamentals-python-library-for-data-science/
